dialogueTree.title: Eugene: ""Didn't Monica have giant titties?""
dialogueTree.polish: „A Monika to nie miała wielkich cycorów?”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "А ў Монікі не было вялікай грудзі?"

dialogueTree.title: Eugene: ""So which one was it, man?""
Eugene: ""We need some *real* music in here.""
Eugene: ""Wish I had my guitar...""
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Я хацеў бы мець тут сваю гітару..."

dialogueTree.title: Eugene: ""I don't do karaoke, man. I'm too g..."
dialogueTree.english: "I don't do karaoke, man. I'm too good."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nie śpiewam karaoke, stary. Za dobry na to jestem”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Я не спяваю караоке, стары. Я занадта добры для гэтага".

dialogueTree.title: Eugene: ""Hardie boys are local legends now.""
Eugene: ""Strange... I even miss Angie's lou..."
dialogueTree.english: "Strange... I even miss Angie's loud stomach..."
dialogueTree.polish: „Dziwne... Tęsknię nawet za hałaśliwym brzuchem Angiego...”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Дзіўна... Я нават сумую па шумным жываце Энжы..."

dialogueTree.title: Eugene: ""Think Mañana could make a good Har..."
dialogueTree.english: "Think Mañana could make a good Hardie boy?"
dialogueTree.polish: „Myślisz, że z Mañany byłby dobry chłopak Hardiego?”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Ты думаеш, што з Маñаны быў бы добры хлапец для Хардзі?"

dialogueTree.title: Eugene: ""Shit like that really makes you th..."
dialogueTree.english: "Shit like that really makes you think."
dialogueTree.polish: „Takie gówno naprawdę zmusza człowieka do myślenia”.

dialogueTree.title: Eugene: ""One day I'll write a song about it.""
dialogueTree.english: "One day I'll write a song about it."
dialogueTree.polish: „Przyjdzie dzień, że napiszę o tym piosenkę”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Прыйдзе дзень, калі я напішу пра гэта песню".

dialogueTree.title: Eugene: ""Goddamn Shanky... never liked that..."
dialogueTree.english: "Goddamn Shanky... never liked that rat-faced fuck."
dialogueTree.polish: „Cholerny Kosior. Nigdy nie lubiłem tego skurwysyńskiego szczura”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Чортовы Касіор. Ніколі не любіў гэтага скунса".
